        <updateDate>2009-11-19T19:27:16Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Indigent Funeral Expense Reimbursement Act of 2009 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a funeral home proprietor a tax deduction for the unreimbursed expense of providing funeral or burial goods and services for a deceased indigent individual. Limits the annual amount of such deduction to $3,000. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
